{%- doc -%}
  Sticky add-to-cart bar — appears at the bottom of the viewport when
  the in-page product form scrolls out of sight. Mirrors the modern
  commerce pattern (Concept's mobile-dock + Essence's sticky-add-to-
  cart) so a customer browsing long PDP content always has a one-tap
  return path to the buy controls.

  R135 / CR-B reject vector — Kitchero previously had no sticky ATC
  surface on PDP, which is a Theme Store competitive-parity gap.

  Renders nothing when:
    • the merchant disabled `show_sticky_atc` on main-product, OR
    • the product has zero variants (gift cards / archived /
      preview-only products).

  The bar starts hidden + inert; product-sticky-bar.js promotes it
  to visible the first time the in-page product form's bounding box
  leaves the viewport, and demotes it again when the form re-enters.
  Both `hidden` AND `inert` are toggled in lockstep with aria-hidden
  so a keyboard / screen-reader user never tabs into an off-screen
  control.

  @param {object} product - Product (defaults to current product context)
  @param {object} section - Section (passes settings through)

  @example
  {%- render 'product-sticky-bar', product: product, section: section -%}
{%- enddoc -%}

{%- if section.settings.show_sticky_atc and product != blank and product.variants.size > 0 -%}
  {{ 'kt-product-sticky-bar.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

  {%- assign sticky_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant -%}
  {%- assign sticky_image = product.featured_media | default: product.featured_image -%}

  <div
    class="kt-pdp-sticky"
    data-pdp-sticky
    data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
    aria-hidden="true"
    hidden
    inert
  >
    <div class="kt-pdp-sticky__inner page-width">
      <div class="kt-pdp-sticky__product">
        {%- if sticky_image != blank -%}
          {{
            sticky_image
            | image_url: width: 96
            | image_tag:
              class: 'kt-pdp-sticky__image',
              loading: 'lazy',
              widths: '48, 96, 144',
              sizes: '48px',
              width: 48,
              height: 48,
              alt: ''
          }}
        {%- else -%}
          {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg kt-pdp-sticky__image' }}
        {%- endif -%}

        <div class="kt-pdp-sticky__text">
          <span class="kt-pdp-sticky__title">{{ product.title | escape }}</span>
          <span class="kt-pdp-sticky__price" data-pdp-sticky-price>
            {%- if sticky_variant.compare_at_price > sticky_variant.price -%}
              <s class="kt-pdp-sticky__price-was">{{ sticky_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</s>
            {%- endif -%}
            <span class="kt-pdp-sticky__price-now">{{ sticky_variant.price | money }}</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button
        type="button"
        class="kt-pdp-sticky__cta"
        data-pdp-sticky-cta
        aria-label="{{ 'kt.product.sticky.cta_aria' | t | default: 'Scroll to add-to-cart' }}"
      >
        <span class="kt-pdp-sticky__cta-label">
          {%- if sticky_variant.available -%}
            {{ 'kt.product.add_to_cart' | t }}
          {%- else -%}
            {{ 'kt.product.sold_out' | t }}
          {%- endif -%}
        </span>
        <svg class="kt-pdp-sticky__cta-icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
          <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="{{ 'product-sticky-bar.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>
{%- endif -%}
